<p>This elevator trip will be significant, so members of the Core Central team will also be housed on site, in state of the art facilities that have been designed to remain cool despite external temperatures.</p>
<p>“The future of interconnected experiences is looking bright,” says Chief Architect Ben Cooper, who was behind the design “but we probably should have installed a few more air conditioners.”</p>
<p>With the unique location in the centre of earth's core, OneQode is building a truly global backbone to support networks around the globe.</p>
<p>OneQode isn't stopping here. Plans are already in motion to build OneQode’s next facility around the sun, which will provide latency-optimised connectivity throughout the solar system.</p>
<h2 class="mt-4">About OneQode</h2>
<p>OneQode is a global infrastructure as a service (IaaS) company operating a latency-optimised international carrier network and high-performance cloud platform designed for the demands of real-time applications and competitive gaming.</p>